global.loginWithDiscordDesc: You need to log in with Discord. Due to recent changes, it's now more difficult to access mutual guilds without being logged in. Please click the login button to continue or [here](https://api.supportmail.dev/login).
global.reportToDeveloper: Please report this issue to the [developer](https://discord.gg/rFkVQx3vpj).

tickets.selectServerDesc: Select a server where you want to continue in an open ticket or create a new one.
